msgstr "倘若你致力於保有電腦運算的自由，那我們推薦這個散布版。"

#: docroot/lib/views/switch_to_linux.choose_a_distribution.php:60
#: docroot/lib/views/switch_to_linux.choose_a_distribution.php:64
